devdoc.details: Provides functions to get the current time and perform time calculations with different time units in Solidity.

returns._0: The current block timestamp in seconds since the Unix epoch.

getTimeMinusOneDay().details: Returns the block timestamp minus one day.

returns._0: The current block timestamp minus 1 day, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

getTimeMinusOneHour().details: Returns the block timestamp minus one hour.

returns._0: The current block timestamp minus 1 hour, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

getTimeMinusOneMinute().details: Returns the block timestamp minus one minute.

returns._0: The current block timestamp minus 1 minute, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

getTimeMinusOneSecond().details: Returns the block timestamp minus one second.

returns._0: The current block timestamp minus 1 second, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

getTimeMinusOneWeek().details: Returns the block timestamp minus one week.

returns._0: The current block timestamp minus 1 week, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@title Time Utility Contract
 @dev Provides functions to get the current time and perform time calculations with different time units in Solidity.

@dev Returns the current block timestamp.
 @return The current block timestamp in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@dev Returns the block timestamp minus one day.
 @return The current block timestamp minus 1 day, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@dev Returns the block timestamp minus one second.
 @return The current block timestamp minus 1 second, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@dev Returns the block timestamp minus one minute.
 @return The current block timestamp minus 1 minute, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@dev Returns the block timestamp minus one hour.
 @return The current block timestamp minus 1 hour, in seconds since the Unix epoch.

@dev Returns the block timestamp minus one week.
 @return The current block timestamp minus 1 week, in seconds since the Unix epoch.
